name: Bella
temperament: Friendly and energetic, responds well to positive reinforcement. Loves treats and playtime. Sometimes gets distracted by other dogs but generally focuses well during training sessions.

name: Max
temperament: Intelligent and loyal, highly trainable with strong focus abilities. Can be protective of family members. Works best with consistent commands and structured training approaches.

name: Luna
temperament: Extremely intelligent and eager to learn. High energy level requires mental stimulation. Excels at complex commands and problem-solving activities. Can become anxious without proper exercise.

name: Rocky
temperament: Calm and patient, but can be stubborn at times. Responds better to gentle encouragement rather than firm commands. Prefers shorter training sessions due to lower energy levels.

name: Daisy
temperament: Playful puppy with lots of energy and enthusiasm. Very food motivated which makes training easier. Still learning basic impulse control and socialization with other dogs and people.
